==English==

===Noun===
'''dingleberry'''  (''plural:'' '''[[dingleberries]]''')
# {{slang}}: A small piece of [[feces]] and/or toilet paper clumped to hair around the [[anus]].  Turds that hang onto dingleberries are called grogans.  They can prove to be quite a problem to Persian cats humans who do not bathe frequently.

